1e8b0334c85f3f539beafe29678","tid":1958633,"uid":239336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b0a124ec3b7ec626a900692635231568501217ec","tid":1958633,"uid":62721,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T19:55:40.000Z","msg":"貼link?成篇post出黎啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T19:57:20.000Z","msg":"任天堂《動物之森》系列最新作 Nintendo Switch《集合啦！動物森友會》（あつまれ どうぶつの森）成為全城機迷熱話，個個爭相入內做奴隸。不過遊戲開售至今半個月，已經有不少無人島開荒者身心疲憊，心頭居然浮現出棄Game之意......<br />\n半個月來玩家過著「另類慢活體驗」，由瘋狂釣鱸魚、刷狼蛛，轉而開始學習炒賣大頭菜來個一夜暴富，結果無數「丁蟹」中伏難翻身；還有單機玩自己、鄰居好樣衰等以下10個難頂體驗，簡直會讓你原地爆炸，寧願果斷棄Game重投現實世界的懷抱。<br />\n<br />\n記者作為忠實玩家，其實也深有體會。例如昨晚到朋友島嶼偷走對方全島水果、到對方花圃瘋狂奔馳等行為（誤），如果發生在自己身上，寧願果斷棄Game絕對冇得傾。不過講還講，其實這些細節也未免不是一種遊戲樂趣，講到尾，有朋友陪你玩，就什麼都會變得好玩。至少......好過單機玩遊戲啊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3823a862cff498fe5d62b940c9acdc2469563887","tid":1958633,"uid":218,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T19:57:31.000Z","msg":"係咪支那出咗隻山寨版<br />\n佢要舖路轉吹奏支那game呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdba917a83099953baa3c0efef4fbe5268659d9f","tid":1958633,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T19:58:22.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨"},{"pid":"c23b176cc56c875ec9af3b005477ada249775742","tid":1958633,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T20:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ef9bdbc925540fb1e26d1118d5ed978dba8fc1","tid":1958633,"uid":116343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff0a4a6c6522ec1ad8a77dd7c6a51aa1c9e9e22e","tid":1958633,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dis